☘️JUST LAUNCHED : Fantasy Garden ☘️
.
.
.

Gossamer wings of dragonflies
platinum petals of tanzanite tulips
sapphire daisies, ruby roses,
amongst million flowers of mandarin garnets.

Red silk wings of butterflies
Multicolored shiny parrots
Tiny little birds , giant bees
over diamond-studded lilies of the valley

Happy pink flamingos
emerald frogs and dancing golden deers
Dreamy flying fish, garnet violets 
around peridot grasses and aquamarine carnations

Metallic fantasies
of an imaginary garden
where dreams meet reality. 
And all life dwells in a 
precious whimsical wonderland.

In between times when Spring melts into Summer and in between places where endless paths converge lies a mystical land where nature turns alive into magical surreal art.

Presenting to you a collection that is an escape from the reality , filled with serene encounters with muses from the natural world that dwell in a precious & whimsical land – The Fantasy Garden.

This collection is a reflection of ephemeral wonders of nature; walks in flower-carpeted meadows, a fanatical trove of creatures, magical moments of fluttering insects, wild flora & tropical birds – all transformed into wearable art. Each piece in this collection is Bold, unique, and adds a touch of tropical whimsy to your wardrobe. Made for the women who love the thrill of new experiences and going wild with her imagination. 

Come traverse into our Fantasy Garden where real and imaginary world blend together with a hint of mystery. ☘️🤍
